《'''Vice'''》是一個美國電視新聞系列節目，製作人為[[比爾·馬艾|比爾·馬艾]]、[[西恩·史密斯|西恩·史密斯]]和艾迪·莫瑞特，並由[[法里德·扎卡利亞|法里德·扎卡利亞]]擔任顧問製作人。這是同名雜誌《[[Vice_(雜誌)|Vice]]》所製播的第一個電視節目，由雜誌工作人員擔任採訪記者。每一集包含數個新聞報導短片，內容涵蓋美國國內和國際議題，主題包括恐怖主義、戰爭、性交易、藥物濫用、武器交易、經濟發展、文化和政治等等。《Vice》在2013年4月5日于[[HBO|HBO]]首播，<ref>{{cite news|last=Lopez|first=Linette|title=What You'll See On The New Vice Media HBO Show Everyone's Been Talking About|url=http://www.businessinsider.com/vice-hbo-premier-2013-4|accessdate=2013-05-01|newspaper=Business Insider|date=2013-04-05|archive-date=2016-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304114326/http://www.businessinsider.com/vice-hbo-premier-2013-4}}</ref><ref>{{cite news|last=Stuever|first=Hank|title=TV preview: HBO's 'Vice' mixes shock and awe with news|url=http://www.post-gazette.com/stories/ae/tv-radio/tv-preview-hbos-vice-mixes-shock-and-awe-with-news-682457/|accessdate=2013-05-01|date=2013-04-07|archive-date=2013-04-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130410040202/http://www.post-gazette.com/stories/ae/tv-radio/tv-preview-hbos-vice-mixes-shock-and-awe-with-news-682457/}}</ref>2020年3月29日起改于[[Showtime電視網|Showtime電視網]]首播。<ref>{{cite web|last=Petski|first=Denise|title=Showtime Acquires ‘Vice’ Weekly Newsmagazine For Spring Premiere|url=https://deadline.com/2019/09/showtime-acquires-vice-weekly-newsmagazine-spring-premiere-hbo-cancellation-1202743499/|website=Deadline|date=2019-09-24|access-date=2020-04-13|archive-date=2022-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220408171140/https://deadline.com/2019/09/showtime-acquires-vice-weekly-newsmagazine-spring-premiere-hbo-cancellation-1202743499/}}</ref>

== 評價 ==
由於其獨特的形式和報導風格，《Vice》同時獲得了正面的負面的評價，有人將此節目與[[荒誕新聞學|荒誕新聞學]]（gonzo journalism）做出比較。<ref>{{cite web|last=Goodman|first=Tim|title=Vice brings its brand of provocative, let’s-go-find-danger journalism to HBO as a half-hour newsmagazine.|url=http://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/vice-tv-review-431808|publisher=Hollywood reporter|accessdate=2013-05-04|archive-date=2021-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308033845/https://www.hollywoodreporter.com/review/vice-tv-review-431808}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Flint|first=Jos|title=HBO's 'Vice' news targets Gen Y with edge and absurdity  From The Detroit News|url=http://www.detroitnews.com/article/20130412/ENT10/304120322|publisher=Detroit News|accessdate=2013-05-04|archive-date=2013-06-15|archive-url=https://archive.is/20130615091314/http://www.detroitnews.com/article/20130412/ENT10/304120322|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

《[[哈芬登郵報|哈芬登郵報]]》上刊載了一篇由莫芮·萊恩（Maureen Ryan）撰寫的負面節目評論，主要針對《Vice》的表現手法提出批評。<ref>{{cite web|last=Ryan|first=Maureen|title='Vice' On HBO: News And Stuff, Bro-Style|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/maureen-ryan/vice-hbo_b_3023038.html|publisher=The Huffington Post|accessdate=2013-04-28|archive-date=2015-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925000642/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/maureen-ryan/vice-hbo_b_3023038.html}}</ref>《[[滾石雜誌|滾石雜誌]]》則評論：「就像是你在酒吧認識的朋友剛好帶了一群攝影團隊跑到阿富汗西邊閑晃。」<ref group="註">"<nowiki>It feels a little like your buddy from the bar just happened to be wandering through eastern Afghanistan with a camera crew.</nowiki>"</ref><ref>{{cite web|last=Van Syckle|first=Katie|title=HBO Courts Danger With Gonzo 'Vice' Show|url=http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/news/hbo-courts-danger-with-gonzo-vice-show-20130405|publisher=Rolling Stone|accessdate=2013-04-28|archive-date=2017-06-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170623133252/http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/news/hbo-courts-danger-with-gonzo-vice-show-20130405}}</ref>

